Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.86,0:00:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yúnchǎng, halt!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.74,0:00:40.58,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(110.455,376.364)\fade(255,0,255,0,380,1540,1820)}Guān Yǔ\NStyled: Yúnchǎng
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.26,0:00:43.18,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(110.455,376.364)\fade(255,0,255,0,340,1620,1900)}Cáo Cāo\NStyled: Mèngdé
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.10,0:00:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yúnchǎng, why are you in such a rush?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.66,0:00:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(360,471.585)}In the past, I submitted myself to you, Chancellor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.64,0:01:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(360,471.585)}Now that I know my master is at Héběi,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.70,0:01:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(360,471.585)}how could I not think of going back?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.65,0:01:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(360,471.585)}I constantly tried to tell you but was never met.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.28,0:01:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(360,471.585)}Hence, I wrote a letter bidding farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.36,0:01:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(360,471.585)}I left my riches and hung my seal to repay you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.35,0:01:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(360,471.585)}I really hope you, sire, did not forget our promises.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.82,0:01:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were to win the trust of the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.82,0:01:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I go back on my words?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.14,0:01:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I fear you might lack some tools,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.18,0:01:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,so here are some gifts for your journey!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.50,0:01:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Chancellor's has been generous, so I do not lack in gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.85,0:02:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Please give this gold to the soldiers instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.12,0:02:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a meager gift is poor \Ncompensation for thy peerless service!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.50,0:02:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Such service is not worth mentioning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.90,0:02:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yúnchǎng, you are a righteous man within the realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.62,0:02:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It is my misfortune that I can't keep you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.75,0:02:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Please accept this silk cloak as a token of my sincerity!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.58,0:03:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Chancellor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.22,0:03:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Many thanks, sire, for this cloak!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.46,0:03:29.46,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(598.295,376.364)\fade(255,0,255,0,340,1620,1980)}Xǔ Chǔ\NStyled: Zhòngkāng
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.65,0:03:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Such an arrogant man! \NWhy can't we seize him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.15,0:03:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yúnchǎng is but one man on one horse, while we are of many!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.44,0:03:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Why wouldn't he be suspicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.19,0:03:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I have spoken. We will not pursue.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.38,0:04:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,How Yúnchǎng fades away...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.54,0:05:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,General Guān!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.44,0:05:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you? Please tell me your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.94,0:05:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I am from Xiāngyáng. My name is{\i1} Liào Huà{\i0}, styled {\i1}Yuánjiǎn!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.26,0:05:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Through these troubled times I've roamed as a drifter
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.56,0:05:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to rob people to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.60,0:05:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Just now, my companion {\i1}Dù Yuǎn{\i0} \Nwent down the mountain to patrol.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.66,0:05:24.14,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(145.227,376.364)\fade(255,0,255,0,340,2180,2460)}Liào Huà\NStyled: Yuánjiǎn
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.99,0:05:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We mistakenly kidnapped\N your ladies up the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.04,0:05:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Only later I learned from my followers they're the Imperial Uncle's wives!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.76,0:05:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I also found out the general was to escort them here,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.90,0:05:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,so I brought them down the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.47,0:05:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet Dù Yuǎn had ill thoughts, wanting to harm them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.24,0:05:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no choice but to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.98,0:05:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I come down to \Nbeg forgiveness from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.52,0:05:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are the two ladies?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.00,0:05:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,General, please look!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.20,0:06:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.50,0:06:22.74,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(190.227,320.727)\fade(255,0,255,0,420,2180,2460)}Lady Mí
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.98,0:06:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Had it not been for General Liao, we would have been shamed by Dù Yuǎn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.94,0:06:28.02,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(96.136,320.727)\fade(255,0,255,0,380,2740,3060)}Lady Gān
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.77,0:06:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.18,0:06:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I have long heard of your esteemed name, sir!\N I am fortunate to meet you today!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.17,0:06:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,If you are willing to, I \Nwould serve you with my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.10,0:07:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You have proven yourself a righteous man.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.02,0:07:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I am lucky to meet you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.10,0:07:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I will repay you for sure in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.86,0:07:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I must seek my lord across a thousand lǐ,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.63,0:07:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,roaming without end,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.93,0:07:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish to escort the two ladies' carriage alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.38,0:07:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If you say such, then I, Liào Huà, must bid farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.22,0:07:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can be of service in the future, I am yours to command!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.59,0:08:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is approaching?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.72,0:08:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the master of the mansion ahead. \NPlease come and have some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.79,0:08:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If so, please allow me to discuss this with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.74,0:08:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I am escorting my two sisters-in-laws
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.28,0:09:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,over a thousand lǐ. It is a heavy responsibility and a long trip,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.05,0:09:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,so please, sire, forgive me for not drinking anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.10,0:09:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,A true hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.96,0:09:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a son named {\i1}Hú Bān,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.49,0:09:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He now serves under the \NAdministrator of Xíngyáng, {\i1}Wáng Zhí.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.86,0:09:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,If you pass through Xíngyáng,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.37,0:09:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a letter to send to my little son.\N May I trouble you with this matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.97,0:09:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I will accept this, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.40,0:10:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,May I ask, good sir, where are we at?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.18,0:10:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Not too far is the choke-point to three provinces, {\i1}Dōnglǐng-Pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.18,0:10:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Many thanks, sire!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.62,0:10:34.42,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(526.705,200.727)\fade(255,0,255,0,420,3460,3780)}Dōnglǐng \NPass
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.68,0:10:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,General, your destination?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.68,0:10:44.54,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(618.75,321.818)\fade(255,0,255,0,360,1520,1840)}Kǒng Xiù
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.34,0:10:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I've bid farewell to the Chancellor and \Nam going to Héběi to find my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.32,0:10:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yes, Yuán Shào of Héběi is the \NChancellor's nemesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.42,0:10:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,For you to pass, you must have \Nthe Chancellor's document.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.36,0:11:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I left in a hurry and was unable to get them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.63,0:11:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Without the documents, \Nyou must stop and settle within the pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.57,0:11:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for me to send for the Chancellor, and then I can let you pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.24,0:11:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If I wait until you send for the Chancellor, would that not delay my journey?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.51,0:11:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.26,0:11:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can't see the Chancellor's documents for a day, then you must wait for a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.85,0:11:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can't see it for a year,\Ngeneral, then you can only wait for a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.46,0:11:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You refuse to give passage to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.59,0:11:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to pass,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.73,0:11:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll have to leave the old and young as a gauge.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.84,0:12:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You dare try to pass?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.86,0:12:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.00,0:12:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop running!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.10,0:12:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no choice but to kill Kǒng Xiù! The rest of you are innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.88,0:12:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I ask of you as witnesses to pass this to Chancellor Cáo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.40,0:12:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell him Kǒng Xiù wanted to harm me, so I killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.34,0:13:35.18,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(623.864,376.364)\fade(255,0,255,0,340,3500,3820)}Luòyáng
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.40,0:13:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Who goes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.64,0:13:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Guān Yǔ. I would walk through this road.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.74,0:13:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have Chancellor Cáo's documents?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.08,0:13:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It is an emergency, I couldn't get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.66,0:14:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I, on the Chancellor's orders, am guarding this place,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.74,0:14:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,especially to investigate spies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.78,0:14:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't have the documents, then you must be a deserter!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.82,0:14:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I live by the honour of my word.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.82,0:14:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I am escorting the Imperial Uncle's two wives and followers only about ten or so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.20,0:14:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Please reconsider, administrator, and allow us passage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.77,0:14:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If not, blades may be drawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.80,0:14:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Blades may be drawn? So what!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.76,0:14:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Kǒng Xiù of Dōnglǐng Pass tried to stop me \Nwithout cause and is now dead by my blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.87,0:14:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Traitor! The audacity!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.44,0:14:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Who wants to capture him together?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.32,0:14:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.50,0:15:15.38,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(387.614,380.727)}Hán Fú
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.62,0:15:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no choice but to fight, I apologize for the horror.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.53,0:16:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Please rise, brother-in-law.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.10,0:16:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, my ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.62,0:17:08.10,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(163.636,433.091)\fade(255,0,255,0,450,4180,4460)}Sìshuǐ \NPass
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.27,0:17:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,General Guān!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.62,0:17:23.78,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(127.841,264)\fade(255,0,255,0,750,1450,2140)}Biàn Xǐ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.28,0:17:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,General Guān, after you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.52,0:17:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Your reputation exceeds you \Nwho wouldn't be awed?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.34,0:17:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you're returning to the \NImperial Uncle! Your loyalty is clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.15,0:17:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,General Biàn, you exaggerate!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.02,0:17:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not. Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.04,0:17:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Since the general was fortunate \Nenough to arrive, I am overjoyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.68,0:18:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I left Xǔdū to find my elder brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.02,0:18:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and there were many dangers along the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.72,0:18:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Who would knew I would meet the pass guards Kǒng Xiù, Hán Fú, and Mèng Tǎn,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.36,0:18:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,who caused trouble without sympathy in my quest to find my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.13,0:18:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They wanted a fight, so I had no choice but to kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.97,0:18:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You were justified!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.44,0:18:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If I see the Chancellor, I'll be sure to exonerate you in front of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.04,0:18:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,General Biàn, you are generous and just. I thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.42,0:18:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You praise me too highly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.08,0:18:51.56,Note (Potential style?),,0,0,0,,Note: Emperor Míng of Hàn, 28 CE to 75 CE
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.73,0:18:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,General, this place, since Emperor Míng's reign, was called the {\i1}Fragrant Flame Garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.22,0:18:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,During Dǒng Zhuó's rule, it was abandoned, but the Chancellor had it rebuilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.24,0:19:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be tired from escorting the two ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.18,0:19:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is exactly where you can find peace and quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.71,0:19:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,General, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.52,0:19:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.82,0:19:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I have already prepared a banquet for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.06,0:19:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, this gentleman has been waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.34,0:19:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,General Guān, how long has it \Nbeen since you have left{\i1} Púdōng?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.34,0:19:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost twenty years.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.68,0:19:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,General, perhaps you remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.20,0:19:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,General Guān, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.57,0:19:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.36,0:19:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.58,0:20:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,General, cheers?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.70,0:20:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.28,0:20:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.12,0:20:18.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The two ladies are still waiting in the carriage—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.84,0:20:21.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Indeed, indeed, let's first serve the two ladies!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.60,0:20:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring tea for the Imperial Uncle's wives.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.00,0:20:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.44,0:20:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,General, cheers?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.13,0:20:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.75,0:20:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What you, sir, have said just now, is that
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.42,0:20:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I, having left for many years, can no longer recognize you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.49,0:20:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed! Indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.86,0:21:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,General, my old home was directly across the river from yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.10,0:21:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish to dine with the general alone, Why are you here blabbering!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.51,0:21:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.71,0:21:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,When old neighbors happen to meet, how could we not reminisce?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.92,0:21:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.82,0:21:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,General Guān, the banquet has been prepared for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.36,0:21:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,General Guān, please come!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.97,0:21:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.11,0:21:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,General Guān, please come!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.62,0:21:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,After you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.92,0:21:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,After you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.44,0:22:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,After you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.65,0:22:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,After you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.78,0:22:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,General Guān!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.54,0:22:42.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,General Biàn, did you invite me out of kindness...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.48,0:22:43.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,... or out of malice?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.53,0:22:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,H-How could there be malice...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.47,0:22:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Get him, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.25,0:23:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,General Guān!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.78,0:23:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you a decent man, yet you dare to do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.42,0:23:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,General! General! Mercy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.65,0:23:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,General! General! Mercy!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.75,0:24:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If not for you, sir, we would have been dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.46,0:24:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no place here to take shelter.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.67,0:24:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You should pack up and search elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.05,0:24:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care, sire.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.88,0:24:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We will meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.69,0:24:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,General, take good care.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.82,0:25:50.10,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(95.114,386.182)\fade(255,0,255,0,380,3940,4260)}Xíngyáng
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.07,0:26:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir, you have escorted your carriage all the way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.18,0:26:10.18,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(92.045,342.545)\fade(255,0,255,0,700,2340,2980)}Wáng Zhí
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.80,0:26:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that there's a place to rest in, \Nwhat harm is there in one cup of wine?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.91,0:26:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, you might not know, administrator,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.81,0:26:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,but considering the two ladies presence, I need to mind myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.15,0:26:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Please forgive me, Administrator.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.99,0:26:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,General, I've long heard of your integrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.99,0:26:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If that is really so, then I won't be forceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.68,0:26:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,If I am being inconvenient, then \NI wouldn't dare trouble you with such an ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.34,0:26:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,General, do as you wish. I will take my leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.11,0:26:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Administrator, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.50,0:27:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Come! Administrator Wáng has brought food and wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.12,0:27:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Let the two ladies eat first.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.12,0:27:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.73,0:27:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonight, get a thousand soldiers\N and surround the inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.13,0:27:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Have every person light a torch and burn it down at the third watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.32,0:27:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Burn everyone on sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.50,0:27:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,, I'll bring troops to support you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.35,0:27:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Once successful, I'll petition the Chancellor \Nto have you rewarded handsomely.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.98,0:27:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall obey your orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.98,0:27:32.66,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(562.5,354.545)\fade(255,0,255,0,700,2060,2660)}Hú Bān
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.25,0:27:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! There, there!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.76,0:27:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.33,0:27:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.20,0:27:53.24,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I've long heard of Guān Yúnchǎng's fame,\Nbut never knew what he looked like.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.71,0:27:56.68,Thinking,,0,0,0,,I must have a look at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.40,0:28:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Truly a man of divinity!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.69,0:28:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.77,0:28:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The subordinate to the administrator of Xíngyáng, {\i1}Hú Bān.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.17,0:28:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you not the son of Lord{\i1} Hú Huá?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.68,0:28:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.89,0:28:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Along the road, your father received me with kindness!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.69,0:28:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Here is his family letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.80,0:28:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You've arrived at a perfect time!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.00,0:28:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, General.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.09,0:29:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,To harm a high-hearted man, would shame my name for generations...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.02,0:29:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,General, please forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.92,0:29:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.15,0:29:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Wáng Zhí wants to harm you in order to avenge his relative, Adminstrator Hán!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.69,0:29:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He's ordered me to surround the inn on all sides, bury you in wood and grass,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.99,0:29:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and set fire at the third watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.46,0:29:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Such vileness... Must be answered with blades drawn!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.00,0:29:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,General! General, Wáng Zhí has made preparations!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.96,0:29:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He has laid an ambush!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.54,0:29:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Though the general is a match for a thousand men, the carriage you escort may come to harm.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.95,0:29:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Better to quickly stow the baggage. I’ll go open the gates.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.42,0:29:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Let the general leave the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.24,0:29:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.72,0:29:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,General, don't delay!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.92,0:30:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Servants!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.54,0:30:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.08,0:30:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Stow the carriage!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.34,0:30:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Please help the ladies escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.18,0:30:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.05,0:30:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.45,0:30:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.67,0:30:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,General Guān!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.55,0:30:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise to repay you in the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.02,0:30:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,General, you need not say more! \NPlease leave now, and take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.62,0:30:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't deserve such grace!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.74,0:31:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Please general, you have to be quick
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.96,0:31:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I must go back to light the fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.96,0:31:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,General, please leave now!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.40,0:31:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Mount your horse!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.37,0:31:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Take good care!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.04,0:31:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.38,0:31:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,General, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.42,0:31:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hú Bān is a kind man.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.55,0:32:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If Wáng Zhí knew of Hú Bān's actions, 
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.06,0:32:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,having us leave the city first, and then lighting the fire, he will surely try to harm him.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.93,0:32:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, General!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.85,0:32:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be Wáng Zhí coming to kill us!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.40,0:32:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You escort the carriage away first. \NLet me deal with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.82,0:32:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Traitor, don't you dare leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.44,0:32:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.66,0:33:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We had no quarrel! \NWhy would you burn us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.10,0:33:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Breaching passes, killing my kin, \Nand you dare say there is no quarrel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.83,0:33:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If you honor my requests, I will let you live.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.23,0:33:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Your subordinate, Hú Bān, is my friend's son.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.44,0:33:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He is a virtuous man!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.24,0:33:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow Hú Bān to accompany me, and this matter is settled.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.65,0:33:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,If not, then it will only take a single blow to take your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.92,0:33:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I did want him to leave with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.69,0:33:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Then that's good. Let Hú Bān come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.90,0:33:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Let Hú Bān out to his quisling master!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.78,0:33:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,For Hú Bān's betrayal, I've seen to his death!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.53,0:33:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead, take his head with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.58,0:33:51.62,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(612.614,380.727)\fade(255,0,255,0,380,1790,2020)}Wáng Zhí
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.96,0:33:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Your life ends here!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.00,0:35:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Second Uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.50,0:36:17.14,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(194.318,429.818)\fade(255,0,255,0,380,3300,3620)}Border of \NHuá Province
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.12,0:36:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,General Guān, Liú Xuándé is currently with Yuán Shào,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.94,0:36:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and Yuán Shào is the Chancellor's rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.71,0:36:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,How could the Chancellor let you go there?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.34,0:36:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then, the Chancellor and I made a promise
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.70,0:37:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If I got news of my elder brother,\N I would join him without hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.99,0:37:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What you have said is what I shall believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.86,0:37:09.74,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(468.409,303.273)\fade(255,0,255,0,750,2180,2860)}Liú Yán
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.85,0:37:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a checkpoint at the Yellow River, but it's guarded by Xiàhóu Dūn's subordinate, {\i1}Qín Qí.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.60,0:37:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Without the Chancellor's documents, \NI'm afraid they won't allow you to ferry.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.44,0:37:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps sir could some prepare the boats for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.61,0:37:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not trying to stop you, but even having \Nthe ships, I fear the Chancellor may punish me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.81,0:37:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't dare oppose him.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.18,0:37:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I happened to save you from danger once.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.60,0:37:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I ask to ferry the river, yet you refuse. Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.76,0:37:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir may not know this, but General Xiàhóu is among the most favoured by the Chancellor.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.30,0:37:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If he knew of this, I will be convicted.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.37,0:37:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,So I cannot pass?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.04,0:37:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot be of assistance.\N My utmost apologies, Yúnchǎng.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.54,0:38:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If your predicament is such, I can only go alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.25,0:38:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.15,0:38:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,General, take good care along the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.38,0:38:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Who approaches?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.68,0:38:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Precinct Marquis of Hànshòu, Guān Yǔ!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.05,0:38:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your destination?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.52,0:38:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish to borrow your boats to search for my elder brother in Héběi.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.62,0:38:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Héběi is in Yuán Shào’s lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.70,0:38:44.38,Style Names,,0,0,0,,{\pos(131.932,373.091)\fade(255,0,255,0,400,3420,3700)}Qín Qí
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.42,0:38:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are the Chancellor's documents?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.39,0:38:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I am no longer under his rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.53,0:38:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would I need it?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.43,0:38:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Under General Xiàhóu's orders, I am guarding this pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.27,0:38:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Without Chancellor's orders, you shall not pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.22,0:38:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you aware of the fates of those who try to stop me?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.91,0:39:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes I have!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.08,0:39:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do know, why do you insist to stop me?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.18,0:39:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,All those killed are but meager rabble!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.22,0:39:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you dare to challenge me?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.60,0:39:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you compare with Yán Liáng or Wén Chǒu?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.04,0:39:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Loose!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.82,0:39:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Spare us! Have mercy!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.06,0:39:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who tried to stop me, is dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.72,0:39:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The rest of you don't need to panic!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.83,0:39:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare a boat for me to cross the river!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.50,0:39:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
